column2: "Hey partner. I'm alright, just leave this to me."
"Nope, I can't do that Yu-nee. You're my sister after all."
"I'm Dark Falz. Dark Falz [Apprentice]. Enemy to all ARKS."
"Please stop this Yu-chan. You don't need to keep on pretending."
"You knew, didn't you, deep down. Even without [Double], you knew something was off."
"The other Dark Falz can command Darkers as well as fight in their powered forms, right?"
"But you didn't Yu-chan, you held back. You commanded them, but you didn't join in on the fight."
"But it wasn't you that did so, was it? Its not that you couldn't, but rather you didn't have the power to do so."
"What do you know? Don't just think you could possible understand!"
"I ask, because I don't understand! If I'm wrong then correct me! And I'll do my best to understand you more!"
"You witnessed me, right partner? She didn't denied any of that."
"To be honest, seeing her run when things get too heated. She hasn't changed at all."
